\n<Rui>I haven't seen a single person up to this point.
Let's ask this child a few questions.
\n<Rui>Eh, oh, now that you mention it, I'm not cold.
\n<Rui>Hey, why are you here in a place like this?
\n<Boy>...Because I can't go inside the house.

\n<Boy>...Yes. I did something bad, so I'm reflecting on
it outside.

\n<Rui>To put a child out of the door in the falling
snow...
\n<Rui>Hey... by any chance, is your name... Tuberose?

\n<Rui>Hmm... Kapala-kun, what kind of bad thing did you
do?

\n<Rui>I see... How long have you been like this? You'll
catch a cold, you know?

\n<Kapala>...I don't know. Ever since my father died, I've
been sleeping outside more often.
\n<Kapala>They say it's better if I'm not around.

\n<Kapala>Everyone hates me. They only play painful games
with me...

\n<Rui>What's that about... Why would they do such
terrible things?

\n<Rui>I don't know the details of Kapala-kun's
situation...

\n<Rui>But there's no way it's okay to leave someone out
in the snow like this.
\n<Kapala>That's quite a selfish thing to say, isn't it?

\n<Rui>...You're right, that was thoughtless of me. I'm
sorry.

\n<Kapala>It's confusing... I feel like I want to be angry,
but at the same time, I'm also happy...

\n<Kapala>I thought all women should just disappear... but
then someone kind like sister would be gone too.
\n<Kapala>Then... kind people like sister would be gone too.
\n<Kapala>But... if I don't kill them, then again...

\n<Kapala>Ah, that's right. The method... I know plenty of
them, don't I?

\n<Kapala>...I just need to make them submit. From the
bottom of their hearts... just like I was until
yesterday.
this.PLLightOn("white2" , 30); //プレイヤーのライトをつける

\n<Golb>Whoa!? What's going on!? Suddenly there's no
interference.

\n<Golb>Yeah, it's the gentle Golb-san. How's it going
over there, Rui-san?

\n<Golb>Is that so? I've scanned the surroundings from
here, but it seems there are only architectural
objects.
this.PLLightOn("tungsten2" , 100); //プレイヤーのライトをつける
